  "texts": [
    "Figure S4 shows the evolution of the weighted total loss L, and the unweighted loss terms L Data, L phys, and L ϕ during the training of the VoF-IcPINNs, optimized for interface re-construction with the sampling and sequential training schemes detailed in the Materials and Methods.",
    "Both phase-field variants of IcPINNs -PF-IcPINNs (no MIM) and PF-IcPINNsshow similar dynamics of losses during training.",
    "As can be seen, the dynamics of L Data and L ϕ behave similarly to the VcPINNs, optimized for velocity and pressure inference, but distinct differences in the dynamics of L phys occur.",
    "As the IcPINNs are optimized for interface reconstruction, more focus was placed on the learning of the phase distribution.",
    "This was achieved by purely data-driven training until the loss for the phase distribution reaches the threshold value L ϕ,T = 0.03."
  ],
